nt|^b@2^z@3
We have now examined 2 of the 3 main situations where a defender can convey an attitude signal about his honor holding in a suit that his partner led by following suit with a high spot card (to encourage), a low spot card (to discourage), or an honor card (to describe his specific honor holding):

|
